parameters:
Okajima: "Suzaku-kun and Shiratora-kun are in... 2nd year
Class B, right? That's Inukai-sensei's class."

Okajima: "I've been observing how all the 2nd year classes
are led by female teachers. Class A has Yamauchi Shion-
sensei, Class B has Inukai Anna Maple-sensei, and Class C
has Anji Rie-sensei."
\F[nako_trouble]Nadeshiko: "The way you say that... is it on purpose?"

Okajima: "Gufufu... Curious, aren't you? That's right. It's
what you call a field experiment."

Okajima: "When a beautiful female teacher becomes the
homeroom teacher, the boys' grades tend to improve! They
become motivated because they want to be praised!"

\F[beni_trouble]Akane: (At least... if Akelnar was my homeroom teacher, I
think my spirits would drop...)

Okajima: "Of course! They'll try their hardest to get close
to her! The power of a teenage boy's fantasies is the most
passionate source of energy!"

\F[nako_true]Nadeshiko: "So you mean they work hard because they don't
want their favorite teacher to dislike them?"

Okajima: "What? You don't get it? Well then... Oh! I have a
perfect example! Washio-sensei!"

Okajima: "Once, we let Washio-sensei take charge of a class,
but there was such fierce protest from the girls that it was
scrapped. They said they were too annoyed by him to
concentrate on their studies!"

Okajima: "If they dislike their homeroom teacher, it affects
their studies that much! So... gufufufu! I thought about
what if it was the opposite!"

Okajima: "It was a great success, wasn't it? If it were
Washio-sensei, the class atmosphere would be gloomy!"

\F[nako_trouble]Nadeshiko: (Yeah... thanks to the sacrifice of the seniors
who ended up in Washio-sensei's class... Thank you.)

Okajima: "Professor Yamauchi Shion, Professor Inukai Anna
Maple, Professor Anjiri Yui... hehehe♪"
